@startuml Employee Lifecycle State Diagram
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam roundcorner 10

title Employee Lifecycle State Machine

state "Onboarding" as Onboarding
state "Active" as Active
state "On Leave" as OnLeave
state "Terminated" as Terminated

[*] --> Onboarding : Employee created

Onboarding --> Active : Onboarding complete
Active --> OnLeave : Start leave
OnLeave --> Active : Return from leave
Active --> Terminated : Terminate employee
OnLeave --> Terminated : Terminate employee
Onboarding --> Terminated : Terminate employee

Terminated --> [*] : Employee removed

note right of Onboarding
  **Initial State:**
  - Employee record created
  - Onboarding process
  - Can assign department
end note

note right of Active
  **Active State:**
  - Employee working
  - Can be assigned tasks
  - Can take leave
end note

note right of OnLeave
  **Leave State:**
  - Employee on leave
  - Can return to active
  - Can be terminated
end note

note right of Terminated
  **Final State:**
  - Employee terminated
  - Cannot be reactivated
  - Record archived
end note

@enduml

